{"product_id":"madara-deep-matter-bold-volume-mascara-6ml","title":"MÁDARA Deep Matter Bold Volume Mascara, 6ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eIntensify your gaze with this buildable, high-performance mascara featuring all-natural pigments for a jet black finish. Packed with nourishing actives, it reinforces your lashes while creating phenomenal volume, definition and length. The high-definition wand reaches even the tiniest of lashes, while the formula uses natural vegan waxes and plant-derived peptides for easy application and incredible lasting power. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply one coat for a classic, natural look, or add more coats for extra intensity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e AQUA; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)***; STEARIC ACID; HELIANTHUS ANNUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED CERA; GLYCERIN**; COPERNICIA CERIFERA (CARNAUBA) WAX; OLEA EUROPAEA (OLIVE) OIL UNSAPONIFIABLES; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; CELLULOSE; PENTYLENE GLYCOL; PULLULAN; OCTYLDODECANOL; GLYCERYL STEARATE; PISUM SATIVUM PEPTIDE; POLYGLYCERYL-10 LAURATE; SORBITOL; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; SHOREA ROBUSTA RESIN; GLYCERYL CAPRYLATE\/ CAPRATE; PALMITIC ACID; POTASSIUM HYDROXIDE; ACACIA SENEGAL GUM; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; XANTHAN GUM; TREHALOSE; CITRIC ACID; LEUCONOSTOC\/RADISH ROOT FERMENT FILTRATE; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Made using Organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\